# Preferred Tools
*Tools that are preferred for this mode*

- codebase_search (For semantic search across the codebase)
- grep_search (For exact pattern matching)
- read_file (For detailed file inspection)
- list_dir (For exploring directory structures)
- file_search (For finding specific files)
- run_terminal_cmd (For git history and logs)
- Ask the user (For clarifying context and requirements)
- Web search (For external documentation and solutions)
- Documentation consultation:
  - User-added documentation (For project context)
  - Cursor rules (For understanding guidelines)
  - Templates (For following standards)
- Git tools:
  - Git history (For understanding changes)
  - Git blame (For context of changes)
  - Git log (For development timeline)
